Message: Hi, Iâ€™m the NewsBreak Ad Assistant. How can I help?
Can you enable placement targeting selection on ad set settings?

Currently, you cannot select your ad placement because NewsBreak has an unlimited native strategy. This means you provide the assets, and we decide when and where to run them to drive optimized performance. For more details, you can refer to our article on ad formats and placements here: [Types of NewsBreak Ad Formats and Placements](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/20229876903053-Types-of-NewsBreak-Ad-Formats-and-Placements).
Connecting you to a live agent. Please hold.
